        "heading": "How To Install",
        "text": "<h2>How To Install</h2><p>[wistia_video]</p><p>To install your new Shower Filter, you'll need the following:</p><ul><li>Qure Shower Filter</li><li>(Optional) Plumber's tape for extra leak protection (provided)</li><li>(Optional) A towel or cloth for better grip when unscrewing the showerhead</li></ul>"
      }
