        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "How To Replace The Filter",
        "text": "<h2>Quick How To Replace The Filter Guide</h2><p>[wistia_video]</p><p>We recommend replacing your filter every 3 months to ensure optimal filtration.</p><p>You may find that water flow slows sooner than this 3 month guideline. In this case, you can replace the filter sooner to maintain strong flow and effective filtration.</p><p>To replace the filter, you'll need a new replacement filter cartridge.</p>"
